### [ SYNC ] Sync cloud infrastructure repo @ https://github.com/mcavallo-git/cloud-infrastructure/blob/master/README.md
*/2 * * * * root /usr/local/sbin/sync_cloud_infrastructure --nginx || curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mcavallo-git/cloud-infrastructure/master/usr/local/sbin/sync_cloud_infrastructure | bash -s -- --nginx;
